 304:src/engine.cpp ****         // Amp decay-to-sustain: s_decay rides 1 â†’ sustain over decay_ms while the
 305:src/engine.cpp ****         // note is gated (stays pinned at 1 when decay_ms == 0, i.e. every other
 306:src/engine.cpp ****         // voice). It scales the gated target so the note plucks down to `sustain`.
 307:src/engine.cpp ****         s_decay = s_decay * s_decay_c + s_sustain * (1.0f - s_decay_c);
