 309:src/engine.cpp ****         // Asymmetric envelope: attack while rising OR decaying-while-held (track the
 310:src/engine.cpp ****         // decay shape quickly â€” its rate comes from s_decay); release only once the
 311:src/engine.cpp ****         // note is actually let go (tamp â†’ 0).
